workouts.title: Barbell Bench Press
workouts.instruction: Lie back on a flat bench.Using a medium width grip(a grip that creates a 90 - degree angle in the middle of the movement between the forearms and the upper arms), lift the bar from the rack and hold it straight over you with your arms locked.This will be your starting position. From the starting position, breathe in and begin coming down slowly until the bar touches your middle chest. After a brief pause
